replies.body: It seems that your OS settings might be preventing the patcher from accessing game files.  As a first step, go over the steps in our [Permissions ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)guide to troubleshoot.  Let me know if that doesn't resolve your issue, and I'd be happy to help!
